metadata.name: Amur Leopard
metadata.description:
Status: Critically Endangered
Amur Leopards are the rarest Big cat in the world with only around 100 left in the wild. They are highly protected animals. Most Amur Leopards are found in Russia and just a few in China.

With buying this NFT, 10% from each sale will be donated to World Wildlife Fund

You have the most artworks purchased from this collection? Let the artist know, which 2 animals should be done as well. You are the creator of this collection.
